Review.Titre: Great Software at Great Price but small problem with Cloud for Documents
Review.Contenu: I really love how affordable this software is. It's exactly what I've been looking for to write and store my work.One small problem I have had is that cloud-saved Documents will occasionally become "jumbled" and some of my recent work has been lost because of this. I've tried going back to a previous save of the document, only to find that some of those have also become jumbled. It is like whole paragraphs have fused with previous ones and some edits don't appear to have been saved, rendering sections of the document unreadable on top of losing recent hard work.So far I haven't had this problem with files saved offline, so I've made sure to do that and it suits me just fine.Other than that problem with cloud-saving, this software has been extremely helpful to me, and the number and quality of the features it offers compared to other alternatives is exceedingly impressive.
